<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Bush </PERSON> <PERSON> Names </PERSON> <PERSON> Kemp </PERSON> as <ORGANIZATION> HUD </ORGANIZATION> Secretary to Seek `` Opportunity Society''
</TEXT>
<NOTE>Eds: Updating with Kemp remarks, inserts new 4th graf, The New, and
