<TEXT>
 A survey finds that 36 of nearly 300 social ministries of the <ORGANIZATION> Evangelical </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Lutheran </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Church </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> America </LOCATION> have special programs for people with AIDS.
