 <PERSON> Larry </PERSON> <PERSON> Margasak </PERSON> spent a week flying on patrols with the <ORGANIZATION> Customs </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Service </ORGANIZATION> surveillance unit in <LOCATION> Corpus </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Christi </LOCATION>. He normally reports on drug issues before <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION>.
